episodes.title: "Breaking the Silence: Apostle Dezra Hines’ Journey from Cult to Calling"
episodes.description:
Apostle Dezra Hines shares her powerful journey of escaping a cult disguised as a holiness church, surviving an arranged and abusive marriage, and reclaiming her voice, purpose, and faith. This episode is raw, real, and redemptive. 💔✨

🎧 Trigger Warning: Spiritual abuse & domestic violence discussed.

🛑 Listen. Reflect. Share. Someone needs this.
